com.google.android.exoplayer2.extractor

Class DefaultExtractorsFactory

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.google.android.exoplayer2.extractor.DefaultExtractorsFactory
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ExtractorsFactory

    public final class DefaultExtractorsFactory
extends Object
implements ExtractorsFactory
    An ExtractorsFactory that provides an array of extractors for the following formats:
    • MP4, including M4A (Mp4Extractor)
    • fMP4 (FragmentedMp4Extractor)
    • Matroska and WebM (MatroskaExtractor)
    • Ogg Vorbis/FLAC (OggExtractor
    • MP3 (Mp3Extractor)
    • AAC (AdtsExtractor)
    • MPEG TS (TsExtractor)
    • MPEG PS (PsExtractor)
    • FLV (FlvExtractor)
    • WAV (WavExtractor)
    • FLAC (only available if the FLAC extension is built and included)
